todos.title: “If your voice is high, only a few people will hear. If your thought is high, then many people will listen.” ~ Invajy
“The bad thing is that the time is short… and the good thing is that there is still some time..” ~ Invajy
“The journey towards success begins with a most important step – just begin” ~ Invajy
“It is during our darkest moments that we must focus to see the light.”~ Aristotle Onassis
“If you’re the smartest person in the room, for sure you’re in the wrong room.” ~ Invajy
“The best things are learnt during the worst days of your life. Get up and see what new learning you had on a bad day.” ~ Invajy
“Always make a total effort, even when the odds are against you.”~ Arnold Palmer
“The best way to get started is to quit talking and begin doing.” ~ Walt Disney
“We are what we repeatedly do. Excellence, then, is not an act, but a habit.”~ Aristotle
“If you talk about it, it’s a dream, if you envision it, it’s possible, but if you schedule it, it’s real.” ~ Tony Robbins
“The pessimist sees difficulty in every opportunity. The optimist sees opportunity in every difficulty.” ~ Winston Churchill
“The best way to predict the future is to create it.” ~ Abraham Lincoln
“Life is not about waiting for the storm to pass; it is about learning to dance in the rain.” ~ Vivian Greene
